"the world's biggest showcase\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"the best athletes\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"the boundaries\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"possibility\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 704}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"leader\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This summer, Intel will accelerate its mission of bringing 'AI Everywhere' using Intel solutions at Paris 2024, showcasing the powerful potential of technology and AI to create immersive and interactive experiences at the Olympic and Paralympic Games Paris 2024 for millions around the world.\\\"\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\", \"score\": 0.9999993680057465, \"rank\": 3.5842182454946556e-07, \"text\": \"Intel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\"}, {\"begin\": 905, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\", \"score\": 0.9999993680057465, \"rank\": 3.5842182454946556e-07, \"text\": \"Intel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\"}, {\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.895627915128107e-17, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its mission\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"AI Everywhere\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"the powerful potential\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 969}, {\"ngram\": \"technology\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"immersive and interactive experiences\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic and Paralympic Games Paris\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1098}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ilario Corna, IOC's chief information technology officer, said in an IOC statement, \\\"Our partnership with Intel has propelled us into a realm where emerging technologies, powered by artificial intelligence, are reshaping the world of sport for spectators, athletes, IOC staff and Partners.\\\"\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6269626988466704e-15, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6269626988466704e-15, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1225, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\", \"score\": 0.9999993680057465, \"rank\": 3.5842182454946556e-07, \"text\": \"Intel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\"}, {\"begin\": 1385, \"end\": 1388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6269626988466704e-15, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ilario Corna\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"Our partnership\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1219}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1247}, {\"ngram\": \"a realm\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"emerging technologies\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"artificial intelligence\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"Partners\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Through their AI-powered solutions, Intel has enabled us to deploy AI faster than ever before.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1448, \"end\": 1453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\", \"score\": 0.9999993680057465, \"rank\": 3.5842182454946556e-07, \"text\": \"Intel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel\"}, {\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.895627915128107e-17, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their AI-powered solutions\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, in Paris, our collaboration will create an Olympic experience like never before, embodying our shared commitment to building a better world through sport,\\\" the statement added.\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1520, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999927060799, \"rank\": 7.293854157393332e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our collaboration\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic experience\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"our shared commitment\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"a better world\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"the statement\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC officials said AI could be used to help identify promising athletes, personalize training methods and make the games fairer by improving judging.\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1699, \"end\": 1702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6269626988466704e-15, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1718, \"end\": 1720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.895627915128107e-17, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"promising athletes\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"training methods\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1819}, {\"ngram\": \"judging\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today we are making another step to ensure the uniqueness of the Olympic Games and the relevance of sport.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another step\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1883}, {\"ngram\": \"the uniqueness\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"the relevance\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1947}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To do this, we have to be leaders of change,\\\" IOC President Thomas Bach said recently at a press event in the velodrome at the Olympic Park in London.\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 2108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2004, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IOC President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2018, \"end\": 2029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 2101, \"end\": 2107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999984909434279, \"rank\": 1.1193109733983627e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"leaders\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"change\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2001}, {\"ngram\": \"a press event\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"the velodrome\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2077}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Park\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are determined t